  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>This sweeping cloak was once worn by an ill-fated Traveler - obsessed with their quest to capture a cosmic leviathan, and doomed to repeat the chase for all eternity.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一套专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>这件宽大的斗篷曾经属于一个命运多舛的旅行者，他痴迷于捕捉一只宇宙巨兽，并注定要永远重复追逐下去。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>改变你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>這件長至拖地的斗篷曾屬於一名命運多舛的旅行者，一心只想捕捉到宇宙龐然大物，注定在永恆的時光中不斷追尋。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
